'''Lynx rufus''' (Schreber, 1777) ({{Vol-en|bobcat}}; {{Vol-ru|рыжая рысь}}; {{Vol-lv|rūsganais lūsis}}) — irā naleļs [[Kaču saime|kaču saimis]] (''Felidae'') plieseigais [[zviers]]. ''Lynx rufus'' dzeivoj Pūstum Amerikā<ref name="ADV">[http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/site/accounts/information/Lynx_rufus.html University of Michigan Museum of Zoology]</ref>.

== Izavierīņs ==
Auguma garums: 65—105 cm<ref name="ADV"/>;</br>
Astes garums: 10—18 cm<ref name=utd>Sparano, Vin T (September 1998). Complete Outdoors Encyclopedia. St. Martin's Press. p. 228. ISBN 0-312-19190-1.</ref>;</br>
Placu augstums: nazkur 58 cm<ref name="ADV"/>;</br>
Svors: nu 4 da 15 kg<ref name="ADV"/>.

